@startuml
title Whisper Mask Client – High-Level Komponentendiagramm

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

actor "User" as User

component "Client Controller" as Controller
component "Audio Capture" as AudioCapture
component "Streaming STT Client" as STTClient
component "AssemblyAI API" as AssemblyAI
component "Transcript Processing" as TranscriptProcessing
component "DeepL API" as DeepL
component "Speech Synthesis" as SpeechSynthesis
component "Google TTS API" as GoogleTTS
component "Audio Playback" as AudioPlayback
component "MQTT Mask Control" as MQTTControl
component "WAV Recording" as WAVRecording

queue "Transcript Queue" as Q1
queue "TTS Queue" as Q2
queue "Playback Queue" as Q3

User --> AudioCapture : speech input

Controller --> AudioCapture
Controller --> STTClient
Controller --> TranscriptProcessing
Controller --> SpeechSynthesis
Controller --> AudioPlayback

AudioCapture --> STTClient : audio stream
STTClient --> AssemblyAI : websocket audio stream
AssemblyAI --> STTClient : transcripts/events

STTClient --> Q1 : complete transcript
TranscriptProcessing --> Q1 : consume
TranscriptProcessing --> DeepL : translate text
DeepL --> TranscriptProcessing : translated text
TranscriptProcessing --> Q2 : enqueue text

SpeechSynthesis --> Q2 : consume
SpeechSynthesis --> GoogleTTS : synthesize
GoogleTTS --> SpeechSynthesis : audio data
SpeechSynthesis --> Q3 : enqueue audio

AudioPlayback --> Q3 : consume
AudioPlayback --> MQTTControl : mouth ON/OFF
AudioCapture --> WAVRecording : raw audio frames
STTClient --> WAVRecording : close session / save recording

@enduml